OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FBBC boss tells India staff 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fto report without fear     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The BBC will not be put off from       
OL,6, reporting without fear or favour, its  
OL,7, Director-General Tim Davie has said in 
OL,8, an email to staff in India.            
OL,10,FIt follows searches at BBC offices in  
OL,11,FDelhi and Mumbai by tax officials.     
OL,13,FMr Davie thanked staff for their       
OL,14,Fcourage and said nothing was more      
OL,15,Fimportant than reporting impartially.  
OL,17,FThe BBC, which is co-operating with the
OL,18,Finvestigation, recently aired a        
OL,19,Fdocumentary critical of Indian Prime   
OL,20,FMinister Narendra Modi.                
